Eggheads Eggdrop Bug Report Form

Eggheads Eggdrop Bug Report Form

  By reporting bugs, you help improve the quality of Eggdrop and make
  it more stable. The more information you provide, the easier it is
  for the development team to fix the bug. Please add everything you
  think is important, in addition to the information requested in this
  form. Thank you.

  IMPORTANT: First check https://github.com/eggheads/eggdrop/issues to
  see if the bug you want to report is already fixed. Also, please
  upgrade to the latest Eggdrop version to see if the bug is fixed
  before reporting.

INSTRUCTIONS

  [1] Complete as many fields as possible.

  [2] Create a new issue at:
      https://github.com/eggheads/eggdrop/issues

      -or-

      Email the completed report to: bugs@eggheads.org

  DO NOT SEND HTML EMAIL.

